The Itare dam project stalled four years ago. Yet I read in the register that, as at June 30, 2018, the outstanding balance on the loan that we borrowed for the project was a massive Sh15 billion, which we must continue paying to the Italian creditor, Intesa Sao Paolo, until September 2034.The thieves are hiding in the register.
